  h1 LES TRANSRISOGRAPHIQUES — EXHIBITION

block project_description
  p.
    A graphic system was created to be declined on several communication supports for our exhibition Transrisographiques by Aurélie Cousquer and Élodie Tourbier.
    All of the supports were using macules that we created during the workshop, on which we printed a simple black layer as an identity.
  p.
    The exhibition at Galerie LENDROIT was divided on different poles and tended to highlight the variety and wealth of the printed posters. The exhibition displayed 
    the several steps of the risograph printing with first the masters used for the different color layers, then the macules used to chock the printing and finally the finished posters.

